{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bd838e129","title":"对美国《新共和》杂志一篇文章的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3184c6fd8b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":26,"articleId":"6bd838e129"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"d837903c8a","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在新华社《参考资料》1957年6月24日第一四三五期封面上。该期第17页至19页刊载了美国《新共和》杂志发表的题为《在我们的对华政策上的辩论》的文章。文章在“跨台论”的小标题下，一开头便说：““一百万人委员会”说：“北京政权现在并不能牢靠地控制住大陆。工业产品、猪肉、棉花和煤的缺乏，反映出一种“严重的经济危机。”毛泽东在旁边批示，“这一句请你研究一下——毛”，并给陈云写了这一批语。"},{"id":"37404d0d63","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4036fc7365","type":"title","text":"对美国《新共和》杂志一篇文章的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129"},{"id":"d837903c8a","type":"paragraph","text":"陈云同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129"},{"id":"37404d0d63","type":"paragraph","text":"17页有一句话，值得研究一下。这一句是唱反调的，但也应当促使我们注意。有人提议农业投资应占20%，少了不利，请你研究一下。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129"},{"id":"1085b04d91","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129"},{"id":"e8bea8a4c1","type":"paragraph","text":"六月廿六日早","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129"}],"page":{"id":"53a4c30c98","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"6bd838e129","start":138,"end":138}}}},"__N_SSG":true}